The council meeting will not be broadcast live due to technical problems
The meeting of the Kouvola City Council cannot be watched live online today.
According to a press release from the city, the shipment is not possible due to technical problems.
The City of Kouvola apologizes for the situation.
The post-recording can be viewed a couple of days after the meeting.
It has been possible to watch the meetings of the Kouvola City Council online since the beginning of the year.
The next time the decision-making can be followed live on 13.10.2014.
The videos of the council meetings can be found at http://www.kouvola.fi/index/aikuisvaestolle/paatoksenteko/valtuustoverkossa.html and on the City of Kouvola's YouTube channel.
